{"tid":1639154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警偷食 PC6570","createTime":"2019-10-08T14:05:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T06:23:48.000Z","uid":275116,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"05b10393d44183bde41462e934aea4992803e359","tid":1639154,"uid":275116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T14:05:36.000Z","msg":"託上託幫post<br />\n<br />\n呢條仆街黑警一直同人講放大假無出過去去左旅行<br />\n但同受騙女事主講: 企喺前面嬲到仆街<br />\n偷食無限loop<br />\n專食有另一半既增加刺激感<br />\n家陣佢條女就係比佢嫁入而要離婚<br />\n做狗做左10幾年仲未有得升就知有幾廢幾垃圾<br />\n<br />\nPS: 女事主而家重比黑警恐嚇，要保護女事主<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hvbTHuu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhvbTHuu.jpg&h=2fcc8495&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VsH7MV9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVsH7MV9.jpg&h=4af94792&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VkMsMWa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVkMsMWa.jpg&h=cb77d368&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ci6Mh2R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCi6Mh2R.jpg&h=d23c2923&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fx2zrWb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFx2zrWb.jpg&h=9eecdb46&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d4eacbb3acce7a964c939eeb994b7adeed4a054","tid":1639154,"uid":251827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:24:40.000Z","msg":"推🤬"},{"pid":"289b24005051f42031c5a311e791e977dd6b22cf","tid":1639154,"uid":23575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:27:38.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ed99701b9c292484ca1b68db938195a46fbbdb48","tid":1639154,"uid":46042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:28:11.000Z","msg":"防暴"},{"pid":"c869f9d5154778afff56b28d1ec930c0e7484fcf","tid":1639154,"uid":34383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10